text: Edmund Trafford (1526–1590), of Trafford, Lancashire, was an English politician. He was a Member (MP) of the Parliament of England for Lancashire in 1572. ==References== Category:1526 births Category:1590 deaths Category:English MPs 1572–1583 Category:People from Trafford (district) Category:Members of the Parliament of England (pre-1707) for Lancashire
